## State Management

- ✅ **Pass state via `WorkflowContext`** — workflow_id, session_id, metadata, state dict
- ❌ **Never use global state** — no module-level mutable variables for workflow data

```python
context = WorkflowContext(
    workflow_id="my-workflow",
    session_id="session-123",
    metadata={"user_id": "u42"},
)
```

